data.description:
Seller is ready for a buyer! You couldn't begin to build a home this size for this price! Come make this spacious home yours!

Are you looking for a home in one of Broken Arrow's premier neighborhoods? Look no further than this one in Deer Creek at Forest Ridge! This home has so much space to enjoy. Large rooms, updated kitchen and an amazing back yard with mature trees. 

This house sits among the manicured neighborhood walking trails, pond and park. You will love the area and love this home.

As you enter the home, you will find a large formal living/dining room on one side of the foyer and the entrance to two bedroom, connected by a jack and Jill bathroom. Perfect for the kids or as an in law suite using one room as a bedroom and one as a living space. 

Continue into the home to view the updated kitchen with backyard views, beautiful granite and a walk in pantry. Connected to the kitchen is a cozy den with fireplace. There is also a convenient half bath. Nestled down the hall is a large primary suite with French doors to the back yard, and a spacious primary bath. 

The second story is like an apartment of it's own- It has a den, bedroom, full bath and hobby or flex room which could easily be a 5th bedroom.

Owner is flexible on closing date, so an out of state buyer or a contingent buyer would be considered.

Other plusses include a large laundry room, extra deep garage for storage, and inground tornado shelter. Set your appointment now!
